data.description: Charming 3 bedroom with PAID SOLAR! This 3 bedroom 2 bath home is just like new, having been built in 2020. It boasts a number of features that make it a dream home for many. With paid solar, you can enjoy the benefits of renewable energy and AC without having to worry about monthly payments. The open floor plan of the home ensures that there is ample space for everyone to move around comfortably. The kitchen is a highlight of the home, with beautiful granite counters, a butcher block island, and stainless appliances. The vaulted ceilings and recessed lighting add to the feeling of spaciousness and brightness. The home also features lovely LVP flooring that is both durable and attractive. Additional storage space is provided by a storage shed, and the finished garage provides even more storage options. Overall, this home is a gem that is sure to appeal to many.
